quran[17{c,v,t}:
23,43,koi qoum nah apne waqt se pehlay khatam hui aur nah is ke baad tehr saki
23,44,"phir hum ne pay Dur pay apne rasool beje jis qoum ke paas bhi is ka rasool aaya, is ne ussay jhatlaya, aur hum aik ke baad aik qoum ko halaak karte chalay gay hatta ke un ko bas afsana hi bana kar chorra phatkaar unn logon par jo imaan nahi laatay !"
23,45,phir hum ne moose aur is ke bhai haroon ko apni nishanion aur khuli sanad ke sath firaon aur is ke a'yane saltanat ki taraf bheja
23,46,magar unhon ne taqqabur kya aur barri dun ki li
23,47,"kehnay lagey"" kya hum apne hi jaisay do admion par imaan le ayen? aur aadmi bhi woh jin ki qoum hamari bandi hai """
23,48,pas unhon ne dono ko jhutla diya aur halaak honay walon mein ja miley
23,49,aur moose ko hum ne kitaab ataa farmai taakay log is se rahnumai haasil karen
23,50,aur Ibn maryam aur is ki maa ko hum ne aik nishaan banaya aur un ko aik satah murtafa par rakha jo itminan ki jagah thi aur chashmay is mein jari thay
23,51,"ae peghambro, khao pak cheeze aur amal karo Saleh , tum jo kuch bhi karte ho, mein is ko khoob jaanta hon"
23,52,"aur yeh tumhari ummat aik hi ummat hai aur mein tumhara rab hon, pas mujhi se tum daro"
23,53,magar baad mein logon ne apne deen ko aapas mein tukre tukre kar liya har giroh ke paas jo kuch hai usi mein woh magan hai
23,54,"acha, to chhorro inhen, doobe rahen apni ghaflat mein aik waqt khaas taq"
23,55,kya yeh samajte hain ke hum jo inhen maal o aulaad se madad diye ja rahay hain
23,56,"to goya inhen bhalaiyan dainay mein sargaram hain? nahi, asal muamlay ka inhen shaoor nahi hai"
23,57,jo apne rab ke khauf se daray rehtay hain
23,58,jo apne rab ki ayaat par imaan laatay hain
23,59,jo apne rab ke sath kisi ko shareek nahi karte
